postReview.title: Sunderland 2-1 Crystal Palace: Stunning Brobbey finish snaps five-game winless run
postReview.description: Further misery was piled on Crystal Palace as they were condemned to a 2-1 defeat against Sunderland at the Stadium of Light.

postReview.title: Sunderland 2-1 Crystal Palace: El golazo de Brobbey corta una racha de cinco partidos sin ganar
postReview.description: Más contratiempos para el Crystal Palace, derrotado 2-1 por el Sunderland en el Stadium of Light.

postReview.title: Sunderland-Crystal Palace 2-1: la prodezza di Brobbey interrompe la serie di cinque gare senza vittorie
postReview.description: Altra amarezza per il Crystal Palace, battuto 2-1 dal Sunderland allo Stadium of Light.

postReview.title: Sunderland 2-1 Crystal Palace: finalização espetacular de Brobbey encerra sequência de cinco jogos sem vitória
postReview.description: A crise do Crystal Palace ganhou mais um capítulo com a derrota por 2 a 1 para o Sunderland no Stadium of Light.

postReview.title: Sunderland 2-1 Crystal Palace : une finition somptueuse de Brobbey met fin à cinq matches sans victoire
postReview.description: Crystal Palace a vécu un nouveau cauchemar, battu 2-1 par Sunderland au Stadium of Light.

postReview.title: Sunderland 2:1 Crystal Palace: Spektakulärer Brobbey-Abschluss beendet fünf Spiele ohne Sieg
postReview.description: Crystal Palace kassierte den nächsten Rückschlag und verlor im Stadium of Light mit 1:2 gegen Sunderland.

postReview.title: سندرلاند 2-1 كريستال بالاس: لمسة بروبي المذهلة تنهي سلسلة من خمس مباريات دون فوز
postReview.description: تواصلت معاناة كريستال بالاس بعدما خسر 2-1 أمام سندرلاند في ملعب النور.

postReview.title: Sunderland 2-1 Crystal Palace: finalização soberba de Brobbey põe fim a série de cinco jogos sem vencer
postReview.description: O Crystal Palace voltou a desiludir ao perder por 2-1 com o Sunderland no Stadium of Light.

preReview.title: Glasner to leave Crystal Palace
preReview.description: Oliver Glasner is out of contract at Crystal Palace at the end of the season, and the Austrian has confirmed he will not be staying on.

preReview.title: Glasner dejará el Crystal Palace
preReview.description: Oliver Glasner acaba contrato en el Crystal Palace al final de la temporada y el austriaco ha confirmado que no seguirá.

preReview.title: Glasner vai deixar o Crystal Palace
preReview.description: Oliver Glasner tem contrato com o Crystal Palace até o fim da temporada e o austríaco confirmou que não vai permanecer.

preReview.title: Glasner lascerà il Crystal Palace
preReview.description: Glasner è in scadenza con il Crystal Palace a fine stagione e ha confermato che non resterà.

preReview.title: Glasner va quitter Crystal Palace
preReview.description: En fin de contrat à Crystal Palace à l’issue de la saison, Oliver Glasner a confirmé qu’il ne prolongerait pas.

preReview.title: غلاسنر يرحل عن كريستال بالاس
preReview.description: ينتهي عقد أوليفر غلاسنر مع كريستال بالاس بنهاية الموسم، وأكد المدرب النمساوي أنه لن يواصل مع النادي.

preReview.title: Glasner verlässt Crystal Palace
preReview.description: Oliver Glasners Vertrag bei Crystal Palace läuft am Saisonende aus, und der Österreicher hat bestätigt, dass er nicht weitermachen wird.

preReview.title: Glasner vai deixar o Crystal Palace
preReview.description: Glasner sai no fim da época e o Crystal Palace já sabe que vai ter de procurar novo treinador.
